Class DynamicRatingListener

java.lang.Object
com.pranavpandey.android.dynamic.rating.listener.DynamicRatingListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
RatingBar.OnRatingBarChangeListener, RatingListener
public abstract class DynamicRatingListener extends Object implements RatingListener
A RatingListener to provide default functionality for the various rating callbacks.
